  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0b9f, \u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0bae\u0bc7\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc2\u0baf\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bb2\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bcd : \u0baa\u0bc1\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd, \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0ba9\u0bcd, \u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bae\u0bcd.\u0baa\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0baa\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc7\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Discussion in New York on North and East Economic Developments: Sreedharan, Charles MPs participate with diaspora representatives",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Following the economic crisis in Sri Lanka, an important discussion has been held in New York regarding plans and future strategies to improve the economy of the North and East.",
        "Members of the Council of World Tamil Organizations, Tamil National Federation's Jaffna Member of Parliament Sivagnanam Sritharan and Vanni Member of Parliament Charles Nirmalanathan and Velanswamy, and Trincomalee Diocese Bishop Noel Emmanuel participated in this discussion.",
        "Sreedharan, Charles and others have gone from Sri Lanka to participate in the \"Maperum Peravaithamith Festival\" organized by the North American Tamil Sangha Council for the 35th year.",
        "In this case, the above meeting was held with the representatives of the Council of World Tamil Organizations. During this meeting, it was clarified by the delegation from Sri Lanka regarding the economic conditions in the north and east of Sri Lanka.",
        "Following this, the diaspora representatives expressed deep concerns regarding the future plans and strategies for economic development of the North-East.",
        "Also, representatives of the Council of World Tamil Organizations, an internationally conducted and monitored independence referendum, an interim international protection mechanism for the Eelam Tamils \u200b\u200bin the north-eastern region of the island until the referendum takes place, promoting worldwide recognition of the Tamil genocide through political arguments and legal means, the United Nations Human Rights Council of Tamil Diaspora. , said that they are working towards the goals of taking legal action against Sri Lanka for genocide crimes against Tamils \u200b\u200bin international court, international court and international countries, creating economic development structures in the Tamil nation in the short and long term for economic development based on Tamil sovereignty.",
        "At the same time, it is noteworthy that steps have been taken for Sritharan and Sauls to hold meetings with the high officials of the US government departments and the Tamil people and organizations living in the American diaspora in this trip."
      ],
